"""
    Get all Host Objects and check if created host is present
    """
api = Icinga2API(username=constants.username, password=constants.password,
    url=constants.url, debug=False)
response = api.hosts.objects()
assert any(res.get('name', None) == constants.TestHost_data['attrs']['name'
    ] for res in response)
pytest.mark.run(order=9)
